1
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:43,280
You've been watching me for a long time.

2
00:01:43,479 --> 00:01:45,009
During the Ghost Festival,

3
00:01:46,240 --> 00:01:48,080
when I was chasing you,

4
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:51,600
you already knew I was your daughter.

5
00:02:00,440 --> 00:02:01,520
Actually,

6
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,680
I have always been secretly watching you.

7
00:02:06,800 --> 00:02:09,400
Especially whenever you cracked a major case,

8
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:11,640
I felt happy,

9
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:13,520
truly happy from the bottom of my heart.

10
00:02:13,520 --> 00:02:17,440
That is also why I haven't left Luoyang for so many years.

11
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:22,040
Li Ze is now in prison,

12
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:25,460
torturing his biological daughter in every possible way.

13
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,460
When the hour of Shen arrives,

14
00:02:27,800 --> 00:02:30,920
he will personally send his daughter to her doom.

15
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:32,560
Then I will go tell him

16
00:02:32,720 --> 00:02:35,840
that Moying is his real daughter.

17
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:40,760
Why are you so sinister and vicious?

18
00:02:44,920 --> 00:02:46,760
I am just a law-abiding citizen.

19
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,680
How could I be sinister and vicious?

20
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:51,520
Inside Luoyang City,

21
00:02:51,640 --> 00:02:54,100
all these major thefts were committed by me.

22
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:56,520
But I've robbed so much treasure,

23
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:58,480
and I've never squandered it.

24
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,200
Neither has Mo Ying.

25
00:03:01,200 --> 00:03:03,440
I gave a lot of treasure and money

26
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:05,440
to the people in the city.

27
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,840
Because back then, your mother and I

28
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,480
also suffered from hunger and cold.

29
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,400
So I swore back then

30
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,320
that one day,

31
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:18,560
I would give this money to those poor people.

32
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:21,840
Am I that sinister and vicious?

33
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,800
But what about Li Ze?

34
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:29,120
He locked me in prison back then.

35
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,600
When your mother was giving birth,

36
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,610
there was no one at home to take care of her.

37
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,800
Died tragically at home.

38
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:39,680
He is so sinister and ruthless.

39
00:03:43,440 --> 00:03:45,280
What about Moying?

40
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:50,400
Do you have absolutely no affection for her?

41
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,200
She is dead.

42
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:57,040
Aren't you even a little bit sad?

43
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,280
Moying

44
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:07,960
had been with me for so many years since childhood,

45
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:10,520
but never enjoyed a good life.

46
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,920
And her only wish

47
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:19,440
was to leave Luoyang City and see the outside world.

48
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:23,880
But as her father, I couldn't even fulfill such a small wish.

49
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,000
If there is a next life,

50
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:34,060
I will repay Moying for this father-daughter bond.

51
00:04:55,760 --> 00:04:56,880
Moya.

52
00:04:58,320 --> 00:05:01,560
Let's see if you will show up or not.

53
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:11,460
It might be a big deal if the execution is halted.

54
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:26,400
Deputy Governor, the time has come.

55
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,240
Execute!

56
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,159
Hold the execution!

57
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:09,960
Jinglan.

58
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:12,580
Did he make things difficult for you?

59
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,800
You're back.

60
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,520
You're back.

61
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,640
I have something to tell you.

62
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,440
My child.

63
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:37,360
Moying is your biological daughter.

64
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:39,360
And I

65
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:42,080
am Moya's child.

66
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,320
Calm down.

67
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,200
I can let you into the execution ground.

68
00:06:55,520 --> 00:06:57,040
But I have one condition.

69
00:06:57,520 --> 00:06:59,400
I need you to face everyone

70
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,200
and tell the truth.

71
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,680
Really?

72
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,720
Yes.

73
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,090
Shaoyin.

74
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,440
Shaoyin Li,

75
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,440
wake up!

76
00:07:21,880 --> 00:07:22,880
Shaoyin Li.

77
00:07:34,640 --> 00:07:35,920
Shaoyin Li.

78
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,480
It's been years. How have you been?

79
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,920
Is what Li Jinglan said

80
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:45,320
true?

81
00:07:47,240 --> 00:07:51,480
Look at our daughter. Does she look like me or you?

82
00:07:59,159 --> 00:08:00,000
Please calm down, Shaoyin.

83
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:02,130
Please calm down, Shaoyin. Calm down.

84
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,360
Yinger.

85
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:38,919
Are you... are you okay?

86
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:44,520
So your plan

87
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:49,360
was to have Li Ze order my execution himself.

88
00:08:50,160 --> 00:08:54,320
Using my life to complete your revenge.

89
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,480
You plotted every step

90
00:08:58,920 --> 00:09:01,800
just for today, didn't you?

91
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:12,000
At the execution ground,

92
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:15,360
I was still worried.

93
00:09:16,480 --> 00:09:18,540
I was afraid you would come to save me.

94
00:09:19,560 --> 00:09:21,120
I was afraid

95
00:09:21,520 --> 00:09:24,160
you'd fall into Li Ze's trap.

96
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,640
Looking back now,

97
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,920
I worried too much.

98
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:36,080
Now I just want to ask you one thing.

99
00:09:37,280 --> 00:09:41,960
Did you ever treat me as your own daughter?

100
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,840
Yes, of course I did.

101
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,640
No, you didn't.

102
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:48,600
If you did, you wouldn't have done this.

103
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,800
Family affection

104
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,000
to me,

105
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:58,640
is nothing but a joke.

106
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:01,480
In your heart,

107
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:05,520
you never treated me as your own daughter.

108
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:10,520
Since childhood, I respected and loved you,

109
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:13,440
and saw you as my only family.

110
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:20,880
But you just treated me as a pawn,

111
00:10:21,040 --> 00:10:22,720
a bait.

112
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:26,320
It's not like that. I love you.

113
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,600
Who knows my heart?

114
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:32,280
How could you be

115
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,880
so hypocritical?

116
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:43,880
If you

117
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:51,280
wanted to see me die in front of Li Ze,

118
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:53,530
then I will grant your wish.

119
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,440
Child!

120
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:04,400
No!

121
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:11,360
All unlawful acts were committed by Moya,

122
00:11:11,400 --> 00:11:12,680
and have nothing to do with Moying.

123
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:15,280
Moya pleads guilty.

124
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,760
Jinglan.

125
00:11:18,760 --> 00:11:19,760
Jinglan.

126
00:11:21,720 --> 00:11:22,840
Jinglan.

127
00:11:24,640 --> 00:11:25,840
Jinglan.

128
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,280
Jinglan.

129
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:32,280
Jinglan.

130
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,520
I've made the bed for you.

131
00:13:10,560 --> 00:13:11,920
You just got caught in the rain,

132
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:13,980
so I also made some brown sugar water.

133
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:17,840
Thank you.

134
00:13:23,160 --> 00:13:24,890
You just got caught in the rain.

135
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:27,400
Drink it before it gets cold.

136
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:40,960
Thank you.

137
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,900
It's raining so heavily outside.

138
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:46,680
If you don't go home,

139
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,920
your father must be worried.

140
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:54,120
If you're not going back,

141
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,760
you can sleep here.

142
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:58,120
I'll sleep over there with the two kids.

143
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:02,440
Thank you for taking me in.

144
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:07,640
But I'm just the daughter of a thief.

145
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:12,000
Whether the blood in my veins is good

146
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:14,400
or evil,

147
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,320
I don't even know myself.

148
00:14:22,480 --> 00:14:24,200
Our friendship

149
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:27,480
is not because your father is Li Ze.

150
00:14:27,880 --> 00:14:29,840
But because you are Li Jinglan.

151
00:14:31,640 --> 00:14:34,840
Even if your biological father is Mo Ya,

152
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,720
it doesn't matter.

153
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:40,120
It won't affect our friendship at all.

154
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:46,320
Look.

155
00:14:47,680 --> 00:14:49,760
You have so many virtues.

156
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,160
Smart,

157
00:14:51,520 --> 00:14:53,800
kind, and brave.

158
00:14:54,040 --> 00:14:57,320
All these traits make up the real you.

159
00:14:57,680 --> 00:14:58,960
Think about me.

160
00:15:00,320 --> 00:15:01,880
When Sister Chunyi died,

161
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,400
I was so sad,

162
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:06,200
but I didn't tell anyone.

163
00:15:08,080 --> 00:15:09,400
But you?

164
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:10,880
You understood me,

165
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,600
empathized with me,

166
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:14,120
stayed by my side,

167
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,610
and even arranged her funeral.

168
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,080
I was very happy.

169
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,640
And the little girl from the Lu Troupe.

170
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:23,440
She yearned for freedom,

171
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:26,240
and you helped me close that case

172
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:28,040
as unsolved.

173
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:29,920
And you?

174
00:15:29,960 --> 00:15:32,600
You were so loud, rushing to the front

175
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:33,920
to keep her safe.

176
00:15:38,120 --> 00:15:39,640
Remember Chen You?

177
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:43,080
The one who always smiled at you.

178
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:45,160
He took such good care of you before.

179
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:47,000
But later?

180
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:50,880
We found out together that he was a hypocrite.

181
00:15:50,920 --> 00:15:52,200
Extremely greedy,

182
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:54,120
and treating human life like dirt.

183
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,360
I didn't expect

184
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:59,800
you to put aside personal feelings and handle the case impartially.

185
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:01,760
I think you must have

186
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:04,240
been very sad back then.

187
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:08,240
A person's sense of right and wrong

188
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:12,000
isn't determined by their background or bloodline.

189
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,800
It lies in your heart.

190
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:17,280
A heart that upholds justice.

191
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:19,440
A kind and honest heart.

192
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,680
Right?

193
00:16:26,640 --> 00:16:28,640
But I'm still very scared.

194
00:16:33,640 --> 00:16:35,760
I'm afraid to face them.

195
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,880
I'm afraid to see my father,

196
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:44,320
and I'm afraid to see him too.

197
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:53,320
If our identities hadn't been switched back then,

198
00:16:56,720 --> 00:16:59,960
Mo Ying might not be the way she is now.

199
00:17:00,640 --> 00:17:01,680
And me.

200
00:17:03,040 --> 00:17:06,800
It's also very likely that he's already a wanted man by the yamen.

201
00:17:10,119 --> 00:17:13,960
Whenever I think of every little thing I shared with my father...

202
00:17:14,520 --> 00:17:17,680
When I was young, he taught me to ride a horse.

203
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,599
He knew I liked boyish things,

204
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:23,040
and bought them all for me. Also,

205
00:17:25,119 --> 00:17:28,400
he indulged me in apprenticing to be a coroner.

206
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:38,720
Whenever I think of these scenes,

207
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:41,200
right before my eyes,

208
00:17:41,760 --> 00:17:45,120
they scatter like fragments.

209
00:17:46,520 --> 00:17:47,960
You know?

210
00:17:48,240 --> 00:17:50,360
I'm really scared to see him.

211
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:53,000
I'm afraid that when I look at him,

212
00:17:54,120 --> 00:17:56,200
he will look at me with strangeness

213
00:17:56,840 --> 00:17:58,120
and alienation.

214
00:17:59,280 --> 00:18:04,040
I'm afraid he'll feel that all these years were wasted.

215
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,720
Do I have no home now?

216
00:18:12,240 --> 00:18:13,240
It's okay.

217
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:14,920
I'm here.

218
00:18:15,840 --> 00:18:18,840
Do I have no home now?

219
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,240
You do.

220
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,400
You have me,

221
00:18:24,680 --> 00:18:25,880
your father,

222
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:28,200
and Mr. Su.

223
00:18:29,080 --> 00:18:30,840
You have so much.

224
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:42,640
Such a beautiful person,

225
00:18:43,440 --> 00:18:44,960
why are you crying so hard?

226
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:48,440
Look,

227
00:18:48,880 --> 00:18:52,560
you just said a lot of what's on your mind.

228
00:18:53,800 --> 00:18:55,960
Shouldn't you tell your father

229
00:18:56,400 --> 00:18:57,640
to let him know

230
00:18:58,080 --> 00:19:00,160
that his tomboy is back?

231
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:06,800
I'll go with you.

232
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:30,120
Look, Jueming is holding Jinglan's hand.

233
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:32,400
I said long ago they would be together.

234
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,600
Exactly.

235
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:41,000
Master.

236
00:19:42,600 --> 00:19:43,680
Take it away.

237
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,320
I can't eat.

238
00:19:51,880 --> 00:19:53,880
Any news about Jinglan?

239
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,160
Everyone went out to look for her.

240
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:59,680
The young lady might be on her way back.

241
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:06,640
Miss.

242
00:20:20,040 --> 00:20:21,400
Go on.

243
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:22,960
He is your father.

244
00:20:24,360 --> 00:20:25,400
Don't be afraid.

245
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:28,400
I will wait for you right here.

246
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,280
Go ahead.

247
00:20:53,320 --> 00:20:54,480
Shijun.

248
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,440
My girl.

249
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:20,880
When your mother passed away,

250
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:23,520
you were still very young.

251
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:26,800
When you learned to speak,

252
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:29,640
the first thing you called me

253
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:32,440
was 'Dad'.

254
00:21:34,360 --> 00:21:36,960
You can't change that now.

255
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:41,380
You've always worried me since you were little.

256
00:21:42,160 --> 00:21:45,480
You loved doing what boys do.

257
00:21:46,560 --> 00:21:50,120
Other girls hold dolls all day,

258
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:51,800
play string instruments,

259
00:21:51,840 --> 00:21:53,600
and do needlework.

260
00:21:53,960 --> 00:21:57,080
But you prefer to tinker with dead things

261
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:59,000
like a tomboy.

262
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:02,680
Other girls would cry in fear when they see a mouse.

263
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:04,680
But your eyes light up,

264
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:06,360
you reach out to catch it,

265
00:22:06,880 --> 00:22:09,040
and play tricks on people.

266
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:11,640
When I pretend to beat you,

267
00:22:11,840 --> 00:22:13,760
you find a corner to hide in.

268
00:22:13,800 --> 00:22:16,330
Poking her head out to scare me and make me mad.

269
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:19,320
Such a special daughter,

270
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:21,960
no one can compare to her.

271
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:24,440
No matter your background,

272
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:26,680
in my heart,

273
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:30,640
you are the most excellent daughter.

274
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:32,520
Daughter.

275
00:22:34,480 --> 00:22:36,680
Daughter.

276
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:40,720
My daughter.

277
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:10,960
Moya.

278
00:23:13,200 --> 00:23:14,720
For revenge,

279
00:23:15,800 --> 00:23:18,560
you pushed everyone into the abyss.

280
00:23:19,360 --> 00:23:20,680
Is it worth it

281
00:23:21,840 --> 00:23:23,120
to do this?

282
00:23:23,760 --> 00:23:25,040
Vice Governor Li,

283
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:27,360
who pushed me

284
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,040
into the abyss

285
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:31,440
back then?

286
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,880
It's my fault.

287
00:23:35,480 --> 00:23:37,160
It's all my fault.

288
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,680
It's my fault for my subjective assumptions

289
00:23:40,680 --> 00:23:42,040
and stubborn prejudices back then,

290
00:23:42,040 --> 00:23:45,920
which caused you to suffer an unjust injustice.

291
00:23:47,040 --> 00:23:51,400
It made you end up like this.

292
00:23:56,200 --> 00:23:58,040
So you also know you were wrong,

293
00:23:58,480 --> 00:23:59,960
Vice Governor.

294
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:03,040
Back then,

295
00:24:04,320 --> 00:24:06,380
when you judged the case at the yamen,

296
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:09,320
you had no solid evidence.

297
00:24:09,640 --> 00:24:11,640
Just based on those old things about me,

298
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,280
you concluded that I was the thief

299
00:24:13,280 --> 00:24:15,320
and locked me up in that prison.

300
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,880
You kept me in prison for a few days,

301
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:22,040
and my wife starved and froze at home for a few days.

302
00:24:22,680 --> 00:24:24,760
In the end, when she was giving birth,

303
00:24:25,640 --> 00:24:27,880
she died tragically at home.

304
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,360
Did you know that?

305
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:30,600
When I begged in prison,

306
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:32,480
who paid attention to me?

307
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:35,280
This is the pain of my life.

308
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,760
And

309
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,120
your saying,

310
00:24:41,560 --> 00:24:44,160
the child of an official is always an official,

311
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:46,560
and the child of a thief is always a thief.

312
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:47,920
Is that so?

313
00:24:49,680 --> 00:24:51,920
Your child could be a thief,

314
00:24:52,040 --> 00:24:54,560
and my child could be an official.

315
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,600
Back then, I secretly swore

316
00:24:56,600 --> 00:24:58,360
I must take this revenge.

317
00:24:58,840 --> 00:25:00,040
My fault.

318
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:02,960
This is all my fault.

319
00:25:04,560 --> 00:25:06,040
But if there's anything,

320
00:25:06,240 --> 00:25:08,080
you can come at me.

321
00:25:08,280 --> 00:25:09,840
You really shouldn't have

322
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:12,600
targeted the two children.

323
00:25:14,280 --> 00:25:15,720
Jinglan, Moying.

324
00:25:15,760 --> 00:25:17,400
They are innocent.

325
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:20,200
They are our own daughters.

326
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:24,280
Is this situation

327
00:25:25,480 --> 00:25:27,680
really what you want?

328
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,320
Then what about my wife?

329
00:25:32,320 --> 00:25:34,240
Wasn't she innocent?

330
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:36,760
Moying.

331
00:25:37,120 --> 00:25:39,080
Moying is also your daughter.

332
00:25:43,000 --> 00:25:45,760
Although Moying has no blood relation with me,

333
00:25:47,320 --> 00:25:50,520
we have depended on each other for so many years.

334
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:53,680
I have long treated her as my own biological daughter.

335
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:56,680
As for Jinglan.

336
00:25:58,560 --> 00:26:00,120
I hope in the future,

337
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:02,920
you can treat both of them well.

338
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:05,280
Moya.

339
00:26:06,120 --> 00:26:07,800
I'm sorry to you.

340
00:26:08,600 --> 00:26:10,660
I plan to resign from my official post

341
00:26:10,880 --> 00:26:12,680
to make up for my mistakes.

342
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:14,920
Don't worry.

343
00:26:15,800 --> 00:26:17,600
After Moying gets out of prison,

344
00:26:18,440 --> 00:26:23,000
I will do everything in my power to take care of her

345
00:26:23,280 --> 00:26:24,480
and protect her.

346
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:29,120
What about Li Jinglan?

347
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:32,240
She is outside.

348
00:26:39,520 --> 00:26:41,280
About the Glazed Pearl,

349
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:43,480
I will only tell her.

350
00:26:47,800 --> 00:26:48,960
Okay.

351
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:55,160
My lord.

352
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:56,880
How is it?

353
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:04,040
Jinglan.

354
00:27:04,800 --> 00:27:06,280
He wants to see you.

355
00:27:07,200 --> 00:27:08,760
About the Glazed Orb,

356
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:12,040
he only wants to tell you.

357
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:22,800
Take care, Lord Li.

358
00:27:28,720 --> 00:27:30,440
I will wait for you outside.

359
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:34,840
Jinglan, hurry!

360
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,880
Go ahead.

361
00:28:08,760 --> 00:28:10,280
As for the Glazed Orb,

362
00:28:11,960 --> 00:28:13,520
it was indeed my doing.

363
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,360
Back then,

364
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:16,920
Yexiao somehow found out

365
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:19,640
the transport route and time of the orb.

366
00:28:20,040 --> 00:28:21,760
We lay in ambush along the way.

367
00:28:22,120 --> 00:28:25,440
After catching the three transport commissioners off guard and drugging them,

368
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:27,400
we found the orb in the brocade box.

369
00:28:30,840 --> 00:28:32,280
As agreed,

370
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:34,080
he gave me a bag of silver

371
00:28:34,360 --> 00:28:37,040
and left with the orb to meet the client.

372
00:28:37,280 --> 00:28:39,400
I never heard from him again.

373
00:28:39,760 --> 00:28:41,240
I figure that by then,

374
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,880
he had already been silenced.

375
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:45,840
And after that,

376
00:28:47,320 --> 00:28:49,450
the matter was never mentioned again.

377
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,440
When he left,

378
00:28:51,560 --> 00:28:53,160
which direction did he go?

379
00:28:55,600 --> 00:28:59,080
Opposite the mountain road is Niutou Mountain.

380
00:29:00,320 --> 00:29:01,800
He probably went

381
00:29:03,800 --> 00:29:05,360
towards the west.

382
00:29:06,960 --> 00:29:08,280
Niutou Mountain.

383
00:29:08,600 --> 00:29:12,440
Cao Wen said Cao Shaoyin also went to Niutou Mountain back then.

384
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:16,160
Could he be the client Yexiao went to meet?

385
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:18,760
On the west side of Niutou Mountain,

386
00:29:18,760 --> 00:29:19,890
there must be clues.

387
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:43,040
We've been digging for three days.

388
00:29:43,040 --> 00:29:44,760
How long are we going to dig?

389
00:29:45,040 --> 00:29:46,040
Stop complaining.

390
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:47,000
Shaoyin has given an order.

391
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:50,060
We must find clues even if we have to level the mountain.

392
00:29:52,160 --> 00:29:54,000
Keep digging.

393
00:29:58,600 --> 00:29:59,480
Jueming,

394
00:29:59,520 --> 00:30:00,800
have a drink first.

395
00:30:00,880 --> 00:30:03,320
Are you sure this is the right place?

396
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,920
Why can't we find it?

397
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:10,080
I'm sure. Let's keep looking.

398
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:12,160
Okay, keep digging.

399
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,920
I'll dig over there.

400
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:14,960
Keep trying hard.

401
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:16,930
Okay, tell me if you find any clues.

402
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:34,720
Found it.

403
00:30:34,760 --> 00:30:35,720
Found a clue.

404
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:39,560
Look around quickly and see if there are any orbs.

405
00:30:39,560 --> 00:30:40,600
Hurry up.

406
00:30:41,960 --> 00:30:42,920
- Dig all around here.
- Okay.

407
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,720
See if there are any orbs. Hurry.

408
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:50,280
Dig here.

409
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,360
Here.

410
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:55,880
Bring it here.

411
00:30:58,280 --> 00:31:01,120
Yes, Su Lang is saved.

412
00:31:01,840 --> 00:31:03,120
The orb is found.

413
00:31:05,840 --> 00:31:07,160
There is also a skeleton.

414
00:31:07,160 --> 00:31:08,040
A skeleton.

415
00:31:08,080 --> 00:31:09,000
Dig and see.

416
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:10,160
Hurry.

417
00:31:16,760 --> 00:31:17,720
What is this?

418
00:31:18,600 --> 00:31:19,760
Let me see.

419
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:22,040
Bring the light.

420
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:30,280
This looks like Constable Qin's sachet.

421
00:31:45,600 --> 00:31:46,680
Are you sure?

422
00:31:46,720 --> 00:31:48,200
Of course I'm sure.

423
00:31:48,280 --> 00:31:50,360
Constable Qin used to carry it every day.

424
00:31:50,360 --> 00:31:51,920
I've seen it many times.

425
00:31:52,600 --> 00:31:55,280
But why would Constable Qin's sachet

426
00:31:55,760 --> 00:31:57,560
be here?

427
00:32:07,600 --> 00:32:08,960
Slow down, Jueming.

428
00:32:28,360 --> 00:32:31,680
Father's remains have been found.

